---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/993422714646941696
  Locus:
    Date: 7 May 2018
---
I often ask myself what is the purpose of our lives and I conclude that
life's purpose is to be happy, We have no guarantee what will happen in
the future, but we live in hope, That's what keeps us going.
